1 inspiring qualities and generosity, and who is now terribly missed but will never be
2 forgotten.
3 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
4 extend its sincere and heartfelt condolences to the family of Jerry O. Arledge on the occasion
5 of his passing and record for posterity his outstanding accomplishments and singular
6 contributions, and does further express its enduring appreciation for the tremendous pride
7 and honor that he will forever bring to his family, friends, players, and state.
8 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to Sally
9 Lytton Arledge.
